    <item>
      <title>尽管市场动荡，日本散户投资者仍表现出韧性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-market-wipeout-hammers-country-s-retail-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年大部分时间，日本股市都为散户投资者带来了丰厚回报，创下新高，并扩大了他们的投资组合。这让一些人即使在过去三天股市崩盘后仍有信心留在股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-market-wipeout-hammers-country-s-retail-investors</guid>
